procprog (0.3-1) lunar; urgency=medium

  * Implement non-scrolling region for statistics, more efficient than
    manually handling scrolling.
  * Add option to fall back to manual scroll handling, some terminals
    (e.g. Windows Terminal) don't handle non-scrolling regions properly
    and delete the history.
  * Fix bugs related to backspace character

 -- Peter Frost <mail@pfrost.me>  Sat, 24 Dec 2022 17:35:41 +0000

